对于worker_cpu_affinity解析
    2核CPU，开启2个进程：
        worker_processes 2; 
        worker_cpu_affinity 01 10;

    2核CPU，开启4进程：
        worker_processes 4; 
        worker_cpu_affinity 01 10 01 10;

    2核CPU，开启8进程：
        worker_processes 8; 
        worker_cpu_affinity 01 10 01 10 01 10 01 10;

    8核CPU，开启2进程：
        worker_processes 2; 
        worker_cpu_affinity 10101010 01010101;

